description:
Freedom of speech is a hot topic in society today. In this clip from the lecture Two Beasts Become Friends, Walter Veith speaks about a future where only a certain type of speech will be allowed. This clip highlights the Papacy being at the forefront of restricting speech, and how America will make an image of this beast.

#shorts #walterveith #freedomofspeech
